{
  "stem": "9728.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Now, I don't know-- because he did not have the shoes, if they thought that he was sick, and he was supposed to go to the-- on the sick transport; or he felt so bad, because we were hungry, and tired, and that he said I don't care anymore, if he willingly went with the sick people because he didn't have the shoes.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "When I came back at night my brother was gone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Now this was the latter part of December.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1944.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I came back, my brother was gone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And since then, I never saw my brother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you can-- you can imagine the effect on this one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You can imagine the effect.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I was-- I was just devastated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, I was with my brother, and now all of a sudden I am all by myself.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At this point, let me go back one more thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Before-- before, when I was still on the first slave labor near Frankfurt [GERMAN], I forgot to mention that I received-- in the ghetto-- in Lodz ghetto we could not have any mail.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We did not receive, or could not mail anybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "However, in camp, we could write and receive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In that camp, I received one and only letter from my parents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was in 1941 at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now coming back to this part, you know, this was the last time that day-- that day when someone stole my brother's shoes, this was the last time that I saw my brother.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never saw my brother again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I-- I had to go to work there the following day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the following day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were chased out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was, as I say, devastated.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
